This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it proposes a memetic algorithm based on particle swarm optimization algorithm (PSO) and pattern search (PS) for SVMs parameters optimization. It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as SVMs are a popular machine learning algorithm. Additionally, it could be classified under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as the proposed algorithm involves optimization and decision-making processes. The paper may also fall under Data Mining (cs.DM) as SVMs are commonly used in data mining applications. Finally, it could be categorized under Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE) as SVMs are used in various engineering and scientific applications.
